<% provide(:title, 'Help') %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
    
    <h4>How to</h4>
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Predict</h5>
        <p>Select Leagues from the main menu. Choose the league you're interested in, and then a match
        from the upcoming matches. Click on Predict. You can only do this up to an hour before kickoff.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">See another user's predictions</h5>
        <p>Select Users from the main menu. Choose a user from the list and on their profile page,
        click on <i>username</i>'s predictions. You will only be shown predictions on matches that are
        no longer open to predicting (either finished or kickoff in an hour or less)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Edit your prediction</h5>
        <p>You can only edit a prediction if kickoff is at least an hour away. Select the match from
        the league matches page and click Edit next to your prediction, or select your prediction
        from the list of all your predictions accessible from your profile page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Edit your profile</h5>
        <p>Select Profile from the Account main menu. Click Edit in the left section under 'Actions'.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h4>Legal</h4>
    
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>It's worth noting that the images used on this site are not owned by me, but
        by the entities which own their respective rights. Many of them are subject to
        copyright restrictions, and I'm only using them in a purely educational and
        non-commercial context. The source of said images is wikipedia.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h4>FYI</h4>
    
    <div class="card mb-2">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>This app's source code is available on <%= link_to 'Github', 'https://github.com/JosephSavioKalule/predictions', target: '_blank' %></p>
        <p>I hope that you enjoy using this app. - Joseph</p>
      </div>
    </div>
        
  </div>
</div>